{"tid":293152,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"NMB48矢倉楓子甜美小惡魔　可愛卻超「胸」","createTime":"2017-06-22T02:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T22:30:17.000Z","uid":38744,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef6ec3cc3e00cccfd53c3a3260bd4dae4c58f66","tid":293152,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=640&amp;q=75&amp;src=http://s.nownews.com/4e/e0/4ee0011d89cc0642a3a1add55f1dd2c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D640%26q%3D75%26src%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2F4e%2Fe0%2F4ee0011d89cc0642a3a1add55f1dd2c8.jpg&h=4fc98752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=640&amp;q=75&amp;src=http://s.nownews.com/media_crop/164123/hash/22/8b/228bf1ac192221af5ad4b913fc2696db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D640%26q%3D75%26src%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2Fmedia_crop%2F164123%2Fhash%2F22%2F8b%2F228bf1ac192221af5ad4b913fc2696db.jpg&h=ed1e98a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本女團NMB48是AKB家族旗下團體之一，團內成員矢倉楓子第一眼就能讓人留下深刻印象，因為出眾的外表受到許多粉絲的追捧，擁有小惡魔般魅力的矢倉楓子除了以偶像身分活動以外，在寫真偶像界也受到不小關注。<br />\n<br />\n今年只有19歲的矢倉楓子，不但單獨拍攝偶像雜誌的寫真，也曾登上多名人氣偶像與演員都登上過的周刊雜誌（講談社）和BUBKA（白夜書房）漫畫雜誌・另外在文化雜誌中也可以看到她的身影。<br />\n<br />\n矢倉楓子最吸引人的地方，不外乎是她那甜美可愛的臉蛋與波浪長捲髮，以及超反差的豐滿胸部，每次登上雜誌的比基尼泳裝照，總能撩的男粉絲魂不守舍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.nownews.com/news/2398280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F2398280&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRezQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=165711dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.nownews.com/news/2398280</a>"},{"pid":"2dff8dbaa84246e7ead4c202d62b66174cfd177f","tid":293152,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"想屌"},{"pid":"940ef8c61e64360ad213831db6edaa22c418b93c","tid":293152,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2